text: James Ormond or Ormonde may refer to: * Jimmy Ormond (born 1977), English cricketer * James Ormond (administrator) (died 1497), Lord High Treasurer of Ireland, 1492–1494 * James Ormond (alpine skier) (born 1973), British alpine skier * James Ormonde (Australian politician) (1903–1970), Australian politician
title: James Ormond
